name: DispatchObject
desc: The base class for most dispatch types.

items.name: func resume()
items.desc: Resumes the invocation of block objects on a dispatch object.

items.name: func suspend()
items.desc: Suspends the invocation of block objects on a dispatch object.

items.name: func setTarget(queue: DispatchQueue?)
items.desc: Specifies the dispatch queue on which to perform work associated with the current object.
